# Build / compose (not needed in OpenCode server image)
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/compose*

# Git / IDE / editor
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.vs
**/.cursor
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.classpath
**/*.*proj.user
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm
**/.toolstarget

# Docs / planning / Cursor memory (OpenCode uses image/AGENTS.md instead)
AGENTS.md
README.md
!README.md
LICENSE
plan_docs/

# Python scaffold (webhook image uses these; opencode Dockerfile does not COPY them)
**/.python-version
**/.venv
tests/

# Host/client scripts (opencode image: entrypoint only; webhook image: prompt wrappers)
scripts/*
!scripts/docker-entrypoint.sh
!scripts/prompt.ps1

# Secrets (mounted at runtime via compose, not baked into image)
auth/

*.code-workspace
.memory/

# Legacy duplicate agent defs (image/.opencode/agents/ is canonical)
image/.opencode/agent/

# Node / build artifacts
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/bin
**/obj
**/charts
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml

# gemini CLI workflows
.gemini/
gha-creds-*.json

# Machine-local agent state
.qwen/
.kilo/
plan_docs/todo.md